                            </p>
                            <p>Talking about an e-commerce business and online selling is the first thing a company wants to do. It must be suitable for the Internet.</p>

                            <p>
                                <h4 class="cizgi">2) Choose the Right eCommerce Infrastructure</h4>
                            </p>
                            <p>People who want to sell clothes online must have a suitable e-commerce infrastructure to set up the e-commerce website after the company has completed the establishment phase. It is very important that the infrastructure you will use on an e-commerce site is reliable. If you want your customers to shop from a secure platform and give them confidence by providing them in this way, you need to find the right e-commerce infrastructure.</p>
                            <p>
